{
  "logNo": "110186846584",
  "title": "우석헌 자연사박물관",
  "addDate": "2014. 3. 10.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110186846584",
  "html_size": 197610,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110186846584\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110186846584\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p>공룡을 좋아하는 나이인 아들을 위해 </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>남양주에 있는 우석헌 자연사박물관을 찾아갑니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_110/isuhani_1394437801114QocQT_JPEG/IMG_7465.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_110/isuhani_1394437801114QocQT_JPEG/IMG_7465.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_110/isuhani_1394437801114QocQT_JPEG/IMG_7465.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>남양주 진접에 있는 우석헌 자연사 박물관 입구.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_42/isuhani_1394437801541fnc3j_JPEG/IMG_7466.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_42/isuhani_1394437801541fnc3j_JPEG/IMG_7466.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_42/isuhani_1394437801541fnc3j_JPEG/IMG_7466.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>공룡화석과 모형들, 그리고 다양한 암석들을 전시해놨다는군요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>입구에 있는 거대한 공룡 모형이 자연사박물관임을 알 수 있게 하네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_23/isuhani_1394437800781BV15s_JPEG/IMG_7464.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20140310_23/isuhani_1394437800781BV15s_JPEG/IMG_7464.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_23/isuhani_1394437800781BV15s_JPEG/IMG_7464.JPG?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>우석헌 자연사박물관 건물 입구에도 공룡이 떡!</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_170/isuhani_1394437801740ErP8n_JPEG/IMG_7467.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_170/isuhani_1394437801740ErP8n_JPEG/IMG_7467.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_170/isuhani_1394437801740ErP8n_JPEG/IMG_7467.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>매표소에서 표를 사서 입장합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_248/isuhani_1394438001811knTiE_JPEG/IMG_7533.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_248/isuhani_1394438001811knTiE_JPEG/IMG_7533.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_248/isuhani_1394438001811knTiE_JPEG/IMG_7533.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>4인가족용 표가 따로 있네요. 13,000원.</p>\r\n<p>대인 표 2매 + 소인 표 2매</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_15/isuhani_1394438002109JdFrk_JPEG/IMG_7534.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_15/isuhani_1394438002109JdFrk_JPEG/IMG_7534.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_15/isuhani_1394438002109JdFrk_JPEG/IMG_7534.JPG?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>입장권에 그려진 삼엽충. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_246/isuhani_1394437801919zI79A_JPEG/IMG_7468.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_246/isuhani_1394437801919zI79A_JPEG/IMG_7468.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_246/isuhani_1394437801919zI79A_JPEG/IMG_7468.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>전시실로 들어가면 선캄브리아시대부터 신생대까지 </p>\r\n<p>다양한 화석들이 질서정연하게 전시되어있어요. </p>\r\n<p>전부다 진품이라고 하네요.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_264/isuhani_13944378020805AzSw_JPEG/IMG_7469.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_264/isuhani_13944378020805AzSw_JPEG/IMG_7469.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_264/isuhani_13944378020805AzSw_JPEG/IMG_7469.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>전시실은 관람하기 좋게 잘 꾸며져 있어요.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_189/isuhani_1394437802253XJky8_JPEG/IMG_7474.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_189/isuhani_1394437802253XJky8_JPEG/IMG_7474.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_189/isuhani_1394437802253XJky8_JPEG/IMG_7474.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>신생대 포유류의 두개골을 보고 좋아하는 아들.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_152/isuhani_1394437802419PzsAC_JPEG/IMG_7478.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_152/isuhani_1394437802419PzsAC_JPEG/IMG_7478.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_152/isuhani_1394437802419PzsAC_JPEG/IMG_7478.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>우석헌자연사박물관은 </p>\r\n<p>각종 생물의 화석과 공룡들 뿐 아니라 </p>\r\n<p>각종 암석, 광석들도 다채롭게 전시되어있더군요.</p>\r\n<p>공룡 뿐 아니라 돌과, 보석에 관심이 많고 좋아라 하는 아들에게는 딱! 맞는 박물관이더군요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_276/isuhani_13944378026172Bmc4_JPEG/IMG_7479.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_276/isuhani_13944378026172Bmc4_JPEG/IMG_7479.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_276/isuhani_13944378026172Bmc4_JPEG/IMG_7479.JPG?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>직원(이 분야를 전공하는 분이라는군요)의 설명 프로그램이 있더군요.</p>\r\n<p>모르고 그냥 갔는데,</p>\r\n<p>오후 2시부터 약 30분간 지구의 탄생에서부터 생물들, 공룡들, 광석까지 쭈욱 훑어가면서 설명해주니 참 좋더군요.</p>\r\n<p>아들이 선생님의 설명을 귀기울여 자세히 듣네요.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_120/isuhani_1394438305581lw6y1_JPEG/IMG_7482.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20140310_120/isuhani_1394438305581lw6y1_JPEG/IMG_7482.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_120/isuhani_1394438305581lw6y1_JPEG/IMG_7482.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>다양한 나이의 아이들이 선생님의 설명을 듣습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_272/isuhani_1394438305897ImGlc_JPEG/IMG_7485.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_272/isuhani_1394438305897ImGlc_JPEG/IMG_7485.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_272/isuhani_1394438305897ImGlc_JPEG/IMG_7485.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>알기 쉽게, 열심히 설명해주셔서 감사~</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_92/isuhani_1394438306269RHdI8_JPEG/IMG_7486.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_92/isuhani_1394438306269RHdI8_JPEG/IMG_7486.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_92/isuhani_1394438306269RHdI8_JPEG/IMG_7486.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>단풍잎 화석.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_196/isuhani_1394438306533YYTA1_JPEG/IMG_7488.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_196/isuhani_1394438306533YYTA1_JPEG/IMG_7488.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_196/isuhani_1394438306533YYTA1_JPEG/IMG_7488.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>물 속에서 살던 공룡의 화석도 잘 보존되어 있네요.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_185/isuhani_1394438306771Ot1oq_JPEG/IMG_7492.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20140310_185/isuhani_1394438306771Ot1oq_JPEG/IMG_7492.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_185/isuhani_1394438306771Ot1oq_JPEG/IMG_7492.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>매머드의 이빨에 대한 설명의 순서까지 왔습니다. </p>\r\n<p>매머드의 어금니는 어린아이 머리통 크기였다는 설명.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_226/isuhani_1394438307010gMO3A_JPEG/IMG_7493.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_226/isuhani_1394438307010gMO3A_JPEG/IMG_7493.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_226/isuhani_1394438307010gMO3A_JPEG/IMG_7493.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>딸은 혀로 자기 어금니를 확인하고, </p>\r\n<p>아들은 손으로 어금니를 만져봅니다. </p>\r\n<p>내 어금니는 어느정도 크기일까?</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_107/isuhani_1394438307268rICDP_JPEG/IMG_7498.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_107/isuhani_1394438307268rICDP_JPEG/IMG_7498.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_107/isuhani_1394438307268rICDP_JPEG/IMG_7498.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>변성암, 퇴적암, 화성암 의 표본들이 잘 전시되어 있습니다. </p>\r\n<p>화석은 퇴적암에서 잘 발견된다는 선생님의 설명.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_179/isuhani_13944383074837nWje_JPEG/IMG_7501.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_179/isuhani_13944383074837nWje_JPEG/IMG_7501.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_179/isuhani_13944383074837nWje_JPEG/IMG_7501.JPG?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>설명 프로그램을 끝내고 야외 전시관으로 이동합니다. </p>\r\n<p>2층으로 올라가야 하네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_265/isuhani_1394439206770f1tPL_JPEG/IMG_7499.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_265/isuhani_1394439206770f1tPL_JPEG/IMG_7499.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_265/isuhani_1394439206770f1tPL_JPEG/IMG_7499.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>2층 가는길에 거대한 초식공룡. </p>\r\n<p>브라키오사우르스?</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_69/isuhani_1394439207239Po4BL_JPEG/IMG_7502.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_69/isuhani_1394439207239Po4BL_JPEG/IMG_7502.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_69/isuhani_1394439207239Po4BL_JPEG/IMG_7502.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>2층 야외전시실에는 다양한 공룡들의 모형이 전시되어 있네요.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_285/isuhani_1394439207722VFDgF_JPEG/IMG_7504.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_285/isuhani_1394439207722VFDgF_JPEG/IMG_7504.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_285/isuhani_1394439207722VFDgF_JPEG/IMG_7504.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>관심없는 딸 ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_217/isuhani_1394439208386ufqi3_JPEG/IMG_7505.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_217/isuhani_1394439208386ufqi3_JPEG/IMG_7505.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_217/isuhani_1394439208386ufqi3_JPEG/IMG_7505.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>2층 야외 전시실을 거쳐가면 박물관 준비실이 있습니다. </p>\r\n<p>정말 많은 표본들을 갖추고 있더군요. </p>\r\n<p>우석헌 자연사박물관은 사설 박물관으로 알고 있는데, 이렇게 많은 표본들을 수집하신 설립자의 노력에 </p>\r\n<p>경의를 표합니다.</p>\r\n<p>(박물관 지하에 백발의 노인이 차를 마시고 계셨는데, 아마도 그분이 설립자이지 않을까 싶더군요. 직원들이 다들 인사하더라구요)</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_286/isuhani_1394439208645xoFG7_JPEG/IMG_7515.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_286/isuhani_1394439208645xoFG7_JPEG/IMG_7515.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_286/isuhani_1394439208645xoFG7_JPEG/IMG_7515.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>자료 보관실을 지나면 또다시 조그마한 전시실이 나오는데,</p>\r\n<p>암석의 형성에 대해 간단하게 알 수 있는 전시물들이 있어요.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_239/isuhani_1394439209207UQFUa_JPEG/IMG_7526.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20140310_239/isuhani_1394439209207UQFUa_JPEG/IMG_7526.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_239/isuhani_1394439209207UQFUa_JPEG/IMG_7526.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>밖에는 하마, 기린 등의 동물 모형들도 있고.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_147/isuhani_13944392095923KFNi_JPEG/IMG_7530.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_147/isuhani_13944392095923KFNi_JPEG/IMG_7530.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_147/isuhani_13944392095923KFNi_JPEG/IMG_7530.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>박물관의 마지막 코스는 체험코스. </p>\r\n<p>암모나이트 화석 지우개를 만들어 봅니다. </p>\r\n<p>1인당 5천원 선불. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_234/isuhani_1394439209833VhhpE_JPEG/IMG_7538.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_234/isuhani_1394439209833VhhpE_JPEG/IMG_7538.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_234/isuhani_1394439209833VhhpE_JPEG/IMG_7538.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></div>\r\n<p>완성된 암모나이트 화석모양 지우개를 손에 들고 좋아하는 아들과</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_200/isuhani_1394439210127Rx4oh_JPEG/IMG_7540.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20140310_200/isuhani_1394439210127Rx4oh_JPEG/IMG_7540.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7A5D978')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140310_200/isuhani_1394439210127Rx4oh_JPEG/IMG_7540.JPG?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>딸. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>지우개는 3개 정도 만들어지네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>큰 기대없이 갔다가 알찬 시간을 보낸 (아들의 입장에서) </p>\r\n<p>우석헌 자연사박물관이었습니다. </p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
